    <briefdescription>
<para>Non-blocking LED controller — blink, flash, patterns. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Drives LEDs through GPIO with non-blocking blink/flash/pattern sequencing. No timers or tasks required — just call <ref refid="syn__led_8h_1a85314d01990c87e390a5c060a6fb3e63" kindref="member">syn_led_update()</ref> from your main loop.</para>
